Interface IVoterData

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    VoterData

    public interface IVoterData
    IVoterData is an interface that represents a voter
    Author:
    Emil

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  IVoterData.AlreadyIdentified
      an exception in case we try to identify the same voter twice
      static class  IVoterData.Unidentified
      an exception in case we try to do illegal operation on non-identified voter like 'markVoted' or 'markStartedVote'
